properties.Name: PhysicalCharacteristic
properties.Description:
A physical characteristic that can be used to identify an individual.

Ex:
- Height
- Weight
- Eye Color
- Hair Color
- Body Type
- Tattoo
- Scar

Columns.Description: The description of a physical characteristic.
